======================================================================
PART 1: DELTA INJECTIVITY FOR INTERIOR VERTICES
======================================================================
For each tournament, for each interior vertex v (1<=d+<=n-2),
check if delta: H_2(T,T\v) -> H_1(T\v) is injective.
(Equiv: all H_1(T\v) cycles remain non-trivial in H_1(T))
